# Paper / publication artifacts.
# The manuscript sources, build artefacts, and review notes stay local.
# The de-identified usability data set is the only paper-related folder
# we publish in this repository, so we whitelist it explicitly. The
# stable DOI for this data set is also minted on the Open Science
# Framework (see docs/paper/data/PUBLISH.md).
docs/paper/*
!docs/paper/data
!docs/paper/data/**
docs/diagrams/

# Operator-private constants (instance URLs, contact persons, wallet
# addresses, hosting credentials). Each adopting institution maintains
# its own copy based on `docs/operators-private.md.example`.
docs/operators-private.md
